{"type":"message","id":"bf48e366","parentId":"5cc8850f","timestamp":"2026-04-13T00:34:01.275Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 🛠️ 正在使用技能列表查询\n\n目前我可以调用以下技能来帮你完成任务：\n\n*   **contact-book**: 通讯录查询（测试环境）\n*   **docx**: Word 文档 (.docx) 的创建、阅读、编辑和转换\n*   **km-operation-prod**: 文件上传、下载及管理（上传到“知聊-我的文件”）\n*   **nickname-lobster-call**: 自定义昵称和对我的称呼\n*   **official-doc-writer**: 党政机关公文生成（通知、报告、请示等，符合国标）\n*   **pptx**: PowerPoint 演示文稿 (.pptx) 的创建、编辑和提取\n*   **self-improvement**: 记录学习、错误和修正，持续自我优化\n*   **skill-creator**: 创建、编辑或审查新的 AgentSkills\n*   **understand-image**: 识别、分析图片内容（包括 OCR 和图表解读）\n*   **xlsx**: 电子表格 (.xlsx/.csv) 的创建、编辑、数据清洗和转换\n\n你想先用哪个技能？或者告诉我你想做什么，我来推荐合适的工具！🦞"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"my-qwen-provider","model":"AIAPLLM-vision-nothink","usage":{"input":18515,"output":249,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":18764,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776040437658,"responseId":"chatcmpl-977d202e-bf07-4acc-b54a-a0a00b387ed4"}}
