{"type":"message","id":"e460bd06","parentId":"edb654ba","timestamp":"2026-04-13T07:31:21.044Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"好的，配置脚本已终止。为了更高效地完成配置，我们可以手动创建配置文件。\n\n请告诉我以下信息，我来帮你配置自定义邮箱服务器：\n\n**IMAP 服务器信息（接收邮件）：**\n1. IMAP 服务器地址（例如：`imap.example.com`）\n2. IMAP 端口（通常是 `993` 或 `143`）\n3. 邮箱账号\n4. 邮箱密码/授权码\n5. 是否使用 TLS/SSL（通常是 `true`）\n\n**SMTP 服务器信息（发送邮件）：**\n6. SMTP 服务器地址（例如：`smtp.example.com`）\n7. SMTP 端口（通常是 `465`、`587` 或 `25`）\n8. SMTP 是否需要加密（通常是 `true` 或 `false`）\n9. 发件人邮箱地址\n\n**可选：**\n10. 默认收件箱名称（通常是 `INBOX`）\n\n请提供这些信息，我来帮你生成配置文件！🦞"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"my-qwen-provider","model":"AIAPLLM-vision-nothink","usage":{"input":29068,"output":224,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":29292,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776065473797,"responseId":"chatcmpl-b0fe0f0a-d54b-948a-a4c8-220989b89e9e"}}
